node.text: “stranger in my brain” featuring @3irty_ dropping on all platforms October 22nd!

My new album “lostnfound” is coming soon! 14 tracks with a lot of awesome features. Also, a music video. I spent over a year on this album and I’m glad it’s finally almost finished. I put everything into this album. I’ll be dropping the track list in the next upcoming week. Love you all ✌️ ❤️

A few weeks ago I lost a really close friend of mine. It’s really sad to see someone who has so much talent and such an infectious personality be taken away by his demons. Talking about this kind of stuff is so hard for me, but I have too. I have 3 unreleased songs him and I made together. At first, I didn’t know what to do with them. I thought maybe because he’s not here it would be inappropriate to drop them, but after some thought I’ve realized he’d want his music out there. I posted a preview of a song him and I did on the last slide. We made this a week before he passed. You can hear the pain in his voice. It’s devastating. RIP @psyoveee
